readme 

This was the input data that was used in both the Qiime and R scripts. 

Metadata_Equol_v2.txt: 

This was the file that included the metadata that was necessary to complete the analysis. 
It includes information on sex and treatment for each sample. 
Sex: M or F 
Treatment: HMB947, HMB947+E, HMB976, HMB976+E (+E indicates the addition of equol producing bacteria) 
